<h5 class="bold">Why use skateboarding shoes? Are skateboarding shoes necessary?</h5>
<p>
  Any experienced skateboarder understands that it is necessary to have skateboarding shoes.
</p>
<p>
  Do experienced football players use hiking shoes to play football? No. Why should it be different with skateboarding?
</p>
<h5 class="bold">Summary</h5>
<p>Make sure you skate with shoes that are intended to be skateboarding shoes. Of course, skateboarding shoes can
come in all shapes and sizes. Some skaters like thicker shoes with more safety but less board feeling - some skaters prefer the opposite.
</p>

